Episode - Class in <Unnamed>
This class will instantiate Episode objects which will contain information about the episode such as the series title it is apart of, the year that series aired, the title of the episode, the number of the episode, and the year the episode aired
Episode() - Constructor for class Episode
Base constructor for this Class with no parameters
Episode(String) - Constructor for class Episode
Main constructor for this class, taking in a single String containing all information on the Episode and passing it to the parse method
episodeNumber - Variable in class Episode
The number of the Episode
episodes - Variable in class Series
A list of all of the episodes of this series
episodeTitle - Variable in class Episode
The title of the Episode
episodeYear - Variable in class Episode
The year the Episode first aired
